# textdomain: mcl_liquids
Allows to change the runtime behaviour of liquids=允许更改液体的运行时行为
This command is used to debug liquid transformation=该命令用于调试液体转换
This command sets the time passed between Luanti ticks.=该命令设置 Luanti 刻之间经过的时间。
If this value is larger than the actual tick, liquids become faster than specified.=若该值大于实际刻数，液体的速度将快于设定值。
